{
  "texts": [
    "Each question was scored in these subdomains on a Likert scale of 1-5.",
    "The average of the two evaluators was taken as the subdomain score of the question.",
    "Comparison Between ChatGPT and Student ScoresChatGPT scores were compared with the average score of the Final Year-Part I students obtained during the internal examination.",
    "To calculate the average score of the students, their deidentified internal examination scores were obtained from the existing departmental registers.",
    "A score of ≥50% is considered the minimum passing percentage for the community medicine subject of the MBBS Final Year-Part I requirements."
  ]
}